Description.SourceString: Known across the colonies as King of the Rails, this heavily armoured train car is designed to protect and exert dominance over contested rail lines, especially when transporting supplies into contested territory as well as safely transporting infantry. This armoured beast boasts a forward facing cannon, as well as heavy lateral guns.
